short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Shows live USD exchange rate for GBP,CAD,EUR,AUD,NZD - every time you open a new tab

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension lets you see every time you open a new tab in chrome, the live exchange rate of USD vs GBP, CAD, EUR, AUD and NZD. 
When clicking on "Reverse", it changes the currency value instead of "USD/____" , into "____/USD".
